Usage: update_oa_lib [-help] <lib_name> [-compress_level <value>]
                     [-create_cdsinfo_tag] [-tech_attach_to_reference]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<lib_name>                    # Specifies the name of a library to be updated
                              # (string, required)
-compress_level <value>       # Sets the compression level of a specified
                              # library (int, optional, min=0, max=9)
-create_cdsinfo_tag           # Adds a cdsinfo.tag file to the specified
                              # library (bool, optional)
-tech_attach_to_reference     # Converts the specified library to use a tech
                              # reference from the attached tech (bool, optional)